	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-175162457" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/09/30/1957234/the-big-shift-from-salaries-to-bonus-based-pay">The Big Shift From Salaries To Bonus-Based Pay</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.msn.com/en-us/money/careersandeducation/the-big-shift-from-salaries-to-bonus-based-pay/ar-AA1rsrBb"  title="External link - https://www.msn.com/en-us/money/careersandeducation/the-big-shift-from-salaries-to-bonus-based-pay/ar-AA1rsrBb" target="_blank"> (msn.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
