		<div id="comment_body_64829395"><p>One thing I note from the idea of a contest is that one party benefits from all the work of the competition entrants but only one entrant benefits when they 'win'.</p><p>Perhaps short-sighted employers will use this type of model soon; "This month 'George' showed outstanding conversions so  his family will eat (for a month)"</p></div>
	</div>

